{"tid":207733,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"「震驚」日本人整塊漏水天花板竟然出動成team人！","createTime":"2017-04-19T05:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-19T17:03:22.000Z","uid":37501,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82ccbde02f1bad66841f25de67dbea3d3d9606c0","tid":207733,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"日本人修補一幅漏水既天花板可以出動成team人<br />\n而且將地板 牆都會貼上防塵膜廢事整到成間屋都係塵<br />\n做完之後成間屋一粒塵都冇 睇完真係好驚啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n工作態度 技術一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完日本人做野片同服務態度我真係覺得其他國家有排都追唔上<br />\n<br />\n如果換成香港師傅 中國師傅<br />\n唔洗問一定係得一個裝修師傅 態度差到仆街<br />\n仲要係你間屋度食煙 整完個天花板唔洗幾個月就會繼續漏水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d-AzARmCbkM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dd-AzARmCbkM&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=ca2364fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d-AzARmCbkM</a>"},{"pid":"ac545f658ec352c0a4feebd4d6066661ec4949a0","tid":207733,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"題外 <br />\n樓上條仆街漏水，又唔俾管理處入屋<br />\n求教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addd113f4658de86cc4adb730f0f5558b80a9cf9","tid":207733,"uid":60935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>題外 <br />\n樓上條仆街漏水，又唔俾管理處入屋<br />\n求教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打1823"},{"pid":"22